<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> kopparakecaripaṉmaṟkku yāṇṭu
<lb n="2"/>16 Āvatu kuṉṟakkūṟṟattu<hi rend="grantha">brahmade</hi>yam ciṟupaḻu
<lb n="3"/>r tiruvālamtuṟai<hi rend="grantha">māhā</hi>tevaṟkku <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kā[<hi rend="grantha">r</hi>]<hi rend="grantha">yya</hi>m Ārākiṟa
<lb n="4"/><hi rend="grantha">kauśika</hi>ṉ nakkaṉ māṟapirāṉ Ārāciyal paḻuvū
<lb n="5"/>r Avaṉikantaṟppapurattu viracoḻa vaṇukka
<lb n="6"/>ṉ kuṇavaṉ <unclear>nakkaṉ vacca</unclear> cantiviḷakku <unclear>munṟu ka</unclear>
<lb n="7"/>lai <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> [<unclear>Iravum pakalum Ākap</unclear>] paṉṉiraṇṭukku
<lb n="8"/>m vaitta po<unclear>ṉ</unclear> pa<unclear>ti</unclear>ṉṉe<unclear>ḻu</unclear> ka<unclear>ḻa</unclear>ñ<unclear>cum</unclear>
<lb n="9"/>ko[[ṇṭu<hi rend="grantha">sandhi</hi>viḷakku panniraṇṭu nakkaṉ]]
<lb n="10"/>{unlegible}
</p>

